Description: Invicta Men's Disney Chronograph Black Stainless Steel Pocket Watch 22747 Time your dreams and wishes with this Limited Edition timepiece from Invicta and Walt Disney collaboration. This men's chronograph pocket watch features a round black dial, white hands and Arabic hour markers. All of these are cased in a black stainless steel case, push crown at the center top and scratch resistant mineral crystal. It also offers a black stainless steel chain secured with hook closure, Japan quartz movement and water resistance up to 30 meters / 99 feet.
